  "title": "Store/Inventory Admin",
  "description": "<p>1. Build and Maintain Store Database</p>\n<p>2. Perform Daily Out-Stock</p>\n<p>3. Order and Replenish Store items</p>\n<p>4. Perform Stock-in</p>\n<p>5. Ensure Cleanliness, Organisation and Compliance for Store</p>\n<p>6. Conduct Monthly Stock Take</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements</strong></p>\n<p>· Candidate should possess at least a Primary/O-Level/A-Level, any field.</p>\n<p>· Able to work independently under minimum supervision.</p>\n<p>· Experience in storing, issuing, shipping and receiving materials and supplies; applying purchasing procedures; applying inventory control methods preferred.</p>",
